data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Located in the sought-after Lake St Charles subdivision, this 4 bedroom/2 bath / 3 car garage/Pool home sits on a conservation lot.  Built by Custom Touch Homes, known for their brick work especially their signature hearth-style cook top area.   Spacious eat in kitchen features built in oven and microwave, bay windows in dinette area, Corian counters and plenty of cabinetry for chef of the house. Solid wood flooring throughout the home, except for two carpeted bedrooms.  Large master bedroom with sizeable master bath area with separate shower and tub spaces.  Enjoy peace and quiet while on the covered screened lanai or floating in the serene pool.  Newer features of the home include ROOF (9/2023), HVAC (2019), water heater (2022), and water softener (2021).  Brand new Epoxy finish in the 3-car garage. LAKE ST CHARLES community offers a community pool, miles of private walking trails, playground, dog park, volleyball, basketball, tennis courts, dock overlooking Lake St. Charles and a clubhouse. LOCATION offers easy access to I-75 and the Crosstown Expressway, MacDill AFB and is a short distance to the Brandon Westfield Mall and to Super Target, Publix and much more.
